      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold as-is, ideal for a buyer looking for a project or a source of parts. The engine requires significant maintenance, and there are noticeable exterior rust spots along with significant wear on the interior upholstery. While it is not currently in reliable driving condition, it offers potential for someone willing to invest the necessary time and repairs.",
